<br />
<br /><div class="quotetitle">Shiru wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">A NESASM bug finally was noticed by me in this project. It does not report ROM overflow in some cases, producing not working ROM without any warnings. If you move some data around, it starts to show an error.</div></div>

